{
  "id": "69cd1f821ba3a660049ae560",
  "title": "親族と遺伝的な類似度",
  "created": 1775050628,
  "updated": 1775054454,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69cd1f821ba3a660049ae560",
      "text": "親族と遺伝的な類似度",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050628,
      "updated": 1775050628
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1f840000000000761081",
      "text": "遺伝子は同様に確からしく配分されるものとしよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050628,
      "updated": 1775050658
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1fa30000000000761083",
      "text": "\tだめか。机上の空論にしても顕性遺伝と潜性遺伝を考慮しないのは",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050660,
      "updated": 1775050724
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1fe50000000000761084",
      "text": "\tそういうのは後で考えればいいや",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050725,
      "updated": 1775050736
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1fef0000000000761085",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775050736,
      "updated": 1775050736
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd1ff00000000000761086",
      "text": "code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
