      "created": 1775051547,
      "updated": 1775052629
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd27520000000000817d75",
      "text": "潜性遺伝子について考慮せずに先祖返りを引き起こせた",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775052627,
      "updated": 1775052826
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd28360000000000817d78",
      "text": "\t37.5 は 25 の親や祖父母世代よりも曾祖父世代 50 に近づいた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775052854,
      "updated": 1775052924
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd27fc0000000000817d77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775052797,
      "updated": 1775053043
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd28fb0000000000817d7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775053051,
      "updated": 1775053051
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd298b0000000000817d94",
      "text": "潜性遺伝について見てみよう",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775053195,
      "updated": 1775053208
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd28e60000000000817d79",
      "text": "code:mermaid",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775053031,
      "updated": 1775053189
    },
    {
      "id": "69cd29850000000000817d7b",
